This is the AmigaGuide® file /help/english/DiskProtection.guide, produced by Makeinfo-1.55 from 
the input file /help/english/DiskProtection.texi.

   This is the documentation for @{b}DiskProtection@{ub}  1.0.

   @{b}DiskProtection@{ub}  is a disk oriented data encryption package for the
Amiga, that encrypts data while writing and decrypts while reading.

   @{b}DiskProtection@{ub}  is shareware and copyright 1994,95 by Patrick Ohly.


@Node Main "/help/english/DiskProtection.guide"

@{i}DiskProtection@{ui}
**************

   @{b}DiskProtection@{ub}  is a data encryption package for the Amiga, that
transparently de- and encrypts data while accessing the disk.

   This manual describes @{b}DiskProtection@{ub}  V1.0.


Introduction
